\begin_inset Formula $\vec{v}^{i}$
\end_inset

 would place them closer to their corresponding anatomical counterparts
 in 
\begin_inset Formula $J^{i}$
\end_inset

.
 Conversely, deforming the image 
\begin_inset Formula $J^{i}$
\end_inset

